  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bottomless Pitfall</strong> is a Simple endless game, where you avoid obstacles in order to get a highscore, and survive the infinite descent.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be Precise and quick.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move with your mouse to steer clear of obstacles and rack up your best score.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy to learn, hard to master!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for a quick time killer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to find out if there’s an end to the pit? Or will you join the ranks of those lost in the Bottomless Pitfall?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bottomless Pitfall</strong> is a Simple endless game, where you avoid obstacles in order to get a highscore, and survive the infinite descent.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Be Precise and quick.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Move with your mouse to steer clear of obstacles and rack up your best score.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Easy to learn, hard to master!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect for a quick time killer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to find out if there’s an end to the pit? Or will you join the ranks of those lost in the Bottomless Pitfall?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
